{"tid":1845020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布 1分鐘後 所有連登會員只可以開同推行動/肺炎post 違例者一律當5毛","createTime":"2020-01-27T02:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T10:40:28.000Z","uid":199590,"like":23,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"873849ac1daee93ca7379d31c6a9e6de105d5562","tid":1845020,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:12:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我屌撚哂你地堆冚家產老母呀！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">熱門全部都係高比Post 搞到行動post推唔郁！！<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘後開始，所有人只可以開同推行動或肺炎post，討論其他嘢必須使用不推文，如有發現不從者，一律當5毛處分<br />\n<br />\n如有任何非行動/肺炎post上熱門，我地連登警察將會入內拉人，並將該名樓主及未有使用不推文的會員一律當5毛</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果呢個post都上唔到熱門，就證明場運動玩撚完，大家可以返屋企打藍波奶共啦！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後一句，光復香港！"},{"pid":"b3f8c4210c4d276532d5b0f1e46da5c78c87f473","tid":1845020,"uid":2040,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:14:01.000Z","msg":"我Kobe迷<br />\n想同時事台大佬拎張今日不抗爭不反對通知書<br />\n得唔得"},{"pid":"0ee0081f85ff2b52da9f45de257f5938fe777d29","tid":1845020,"uid":199590,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:14:53.000Z","msg":"你堆冚家產攪到行動post上唔到熱門啦，你地到底知唔知連登熱門對我地成場運動有幾咁重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7193db10af9f9ce66bbb9d30ab669b72c076155","tid":1845020,"uid":199590,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b3f8c4210c4d276532d5b0f1e46da5c78c87f473","tid":1845020,"uid":2040,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:14:01.000Z","msg":"我Kobe迷<br />\n想同時事台大佬拎張今日不抗爭不反對通知書<br />\n得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"唔批"},{"pid":"fe7f37bb1aeb8116d31c0db1e3eaebe572f59fc4","tid":1845020,"uid":201398,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:15:34.000Z","msg":"你話事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/do